Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit Introducing our luxurious Cosy Loungewear Collection
- the ultimate loungewear for summer. Made from a unique blend of viscose, polyester, and elastane,
this collection boasts a buttery-soft, ultra-comfortable knitted jersey fabric that feels as amazing
as it looks.Experience the epitome of comfort and style with our easy-breezy silhouettes and wide
range of colors, perfect for lounging around the house or running errands in style. The attention to
detail is reflected in every piece, from the delicate stitching to the luxurious texture of the
fabric.Whether you're curling up with a good book or entertaining guests, our Cosy Loungewear
Collection is sure to impress. Relax in style and stay cool and comfortable during hot summer days
with this premium collection. Elevate your loungewear game and shop our collection today. Fabric :
Knitted jersey in an unique blend of viscose polyester & elastane | 190 GSM.Care : Machine wash
according to instructions on care label.

title: Summer Breeze Co-ord Set
description:
Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit A sophisticated monochromatic set, consisting of a
timeless t-shirt and elegant shorts. The t-shirt features a sleek crew neckline and chic half
sleeves, elevated by striking V-shaped rib cut panel details. The knee-length shorts boast a refined
mid-rise fit, adjustable waist with drawcord accents, and two practical side pockets. A fusion of
style and functionality, this set is a must-have for the fashion-forward individual.Fabric: Soft,
Stretchy Baby Fleece. 100% rich, breathable cotton | 240 GSM. Care : Machine wash according to
instructions on the care label.
